Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.11,0:01:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真广
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.23,0:01:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想这么问我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.81,0:01:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能成为我的女人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.51,0:01:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 我还不至于那么没品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.82,0:01:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你到底想和妹妹变成什么关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.01,0:01:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.48,0:01:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从没把我当哥哥看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.23,0:02:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们又没血缘关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.90,0:02:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 为什么会是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.78,0:02:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不合理了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一直以来交往过的女生完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.07,0:02:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没姿色又没胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.89,0:02:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会对你那么在意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越想越不淡定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.10,0:02:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是睡眠不足哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.98,0:02:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.73,0:02:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之你暂时不要和别人扯上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖听我话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.51,0:02:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我已经和某人扯上关系了 你会怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.36,0:02:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难…难道你已经有男朋友了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.03,0:02:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照合理思维来想的话 到底有没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.89,0:02:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爱指引着命运呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:03:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是命运指引着爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.18,0:03:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥冥之中考验着我们的人生之难题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:20.82,每集标题,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(643,476)}初吻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防寒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让寒风渗进来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶风小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.91,0:03:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说决战前得好好养养神什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正又是喝醉了 睡的正香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.21,0:03:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.72,0:03:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪里弄到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从上次我们借宿的人家里借来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.41,0:04:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真厉害 见缝插针的神偷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是借用一下而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用完会还回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一切结束之后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切…结束之后？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管结果如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的不合理之事将会马上被纠正
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦找到杀死爱花的凶手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真广一定会毫不犹豫地亲手了结他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的真广就只为此而活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复仇完毕之后再做何打算呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久不见你这样了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前老盯着手机看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近几乎不这样了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是冷得火大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天很闷热…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.04,0:05:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱花啊 你还有这么多作业没做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为大暑假的不让人好好休息 还一大堆作业
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.28,0:05:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不合理了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.29,0:05:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夏天结束之前试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:05:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我可不想在这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.68,0:06:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么想来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.18,0:06:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是想挑个好地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.53,0:06:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野有什么建议吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？ 突然问我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.17,0:06:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 爱花有什么想法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道有个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别墅？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.66,0:06:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年暑假的最后一周 我们全家都会一起过的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要叫我也去那里？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.96,0:06:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父母肯定会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.88,0:06:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 居然要和真广一起住一周啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也和我一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野 请你和真广好好相处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和那人交朋友的 也只有吉野你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.55,0:07:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经察觉到真广的心意了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真广
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闲着吧 现在到车站来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.40,0:07:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别突然就一口咬定我很闲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.65,0:07:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 10分钟后见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10分钟？  这也太赶了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.89,0:07:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.19,0:07:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 真广…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来介绍一下 这家伙叫泷川吉野
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野君？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不常见的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…我果然还有事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.28,0:07:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那咱们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold不住了 我萌上姐弟恋了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:52.63,Default top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是和同龄人交往好无趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真广 这么做不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:54.32,Default top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好又怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正中红心！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.57,0:08:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅爆了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 两个人都好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是职业级别的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.41,0:08:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.51,0:08:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BYE BYE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.42,0:08:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再做这种事了 我会很头大的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家难得想给你介绍个女朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁拜托过你那种事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的还真是轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙的性格我要不多管管 什么时候才…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:09:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友可不是想要找一个才去交往的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.11,0:09:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和她在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.05,0:09:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才想让她成为自己的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是恋爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.65,0:09:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时间才回家 还真是悠闲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.12,0:09:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让吉野陪了我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.75,0:09:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他差不多也该想找个妹子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.43,0:09:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想给他介绍一个来着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过他貌似很不情愿的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,0:09:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种人的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该和吉野同学合不来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话可不能这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.88,0:10:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身边可是有几位妙龄女大学生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想用筷子戳你的锁骨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.47,0:10:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性情怪癖到会说这种话的吉野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得妙龄女大学生会受得了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对吉野这小子也太多偏见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.18,0:10:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好听点 吉野同学是适应性强
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不好听点 就是没个性
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论身处多么恶劣的环境
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他都能处之泰然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己却不会积极主动地去改变现状
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是那种主动出击 把女生追到手的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反倒要女生倒过来追他才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.83,0:10:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般的女生遇上这种不干脆的人 避之不及呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那倒也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.89,0:10:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和吉野相配的应该是像你这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.27,0:10:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:11:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放荡不羁 我行我素
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.54,0:11:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都按照自己的想法行事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人被你耍得团团转 你却完全不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟王公贵族一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野和你这种人在一起再合适不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.47,0:11:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说这么恶心的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是说男人之间的交往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思是 这世上没有女生能像你这么傲慢专横
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽这么说 你还是要好好珍惜吉野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.82,0:11:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为无论发生什么 他都会和你并肩作战
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是服了真广了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说他已经觉察到我和爱花的事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才硬要给我介绍对象
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 应该不会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙明明第六感很强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:12:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可关键时候却很迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.02,0:12:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱花！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对兄妹真是太会捉弄人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:14.84,sign 黑体,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42\frz6.419\pos(672,542)}女大学生的锁骨怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你的感官那么敏感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么敏感不敏感的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是富家公子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.43,0:12:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是爱炫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.27,0:12:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.73,0:12:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是和自己喜欢的女生交往的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算把人追到手上了也没什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过…那种话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:13:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…我还是不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为总是别人先找我搭讪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和自己喜欢的女孩交往是什么感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.95,0:13:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管交往得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终还是会分手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.33,0:13:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和自己喜欢的人交往
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还去考虑这些问题不是太残酷了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.69,0:13:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星 真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前也一起看过星星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我家的别墅吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 暑假的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？ 你不是说过讨厌星星的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢冬天的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛然威严而又冷艳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:14:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近在眼前却又高高在上触手不及
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.08,0:14:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真广可能一生都察觉不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己只是喜欢上了爱花
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.42,0:14:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样狂妄的真广
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍稍碰触到爱花都会紧张到不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在她身边却又会不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.83,0:14:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱花虽然嘴上没说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定也不讨厌真广吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们不是如此相遇 或许他们会…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 真广
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱花
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.27,0:15:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！ 真是麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力所能及的事就要自己动手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是爸爸的教育方针哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你父母竟然不能过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 因为有工作走不开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 吉野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有空的话 把楼梯也擦一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是讨厌吉野啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.01,0:15:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才请那家伙来别墅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽情的玩弄他 拿他来解闷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说 你有什么阴谋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阴谋？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定还真有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭丫头 一下子放那么多的话会烤焦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真广才是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该刷好酱料再烤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.11,0:15:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算啦算啦 享受美食时就开心点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我来烤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.34,0:16:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来烤玉米吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.34,0:16:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也想吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:18.50,sign 黑体,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\c&H414141&\frz8.922\pos(654,629)}吃完饭后 我们在后院碰面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤焦了啊 吉野
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们居住的城镇里 看不到这么美的星空呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来没看过这么多的星星呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.26,0:16:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是要溢出天空一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.51,0:16:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日的星空真是很没节操呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.38,0:16:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡乱一气地闪耀着光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:16:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱花讨厌星星吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼命炫耀自己的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望在自己逝去的瞬间 有人能意识到自己存在过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢这种耿直的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.83,0:17:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野 你在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱花也在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野 你在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.86,0:17:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们搞什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来玩扑克吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来别墅玩当然首选扑克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那输了的人就得做早餐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:17:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要掺一脚吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.02,0:18:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你们俩刚才在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.14,0:18:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…看星星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我拿夏季的星星很没辙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.74,0:18:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无节操的乱闪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脖子有点痒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.31,0:18:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回屋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.44,0:18:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请调成振动哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 气死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.13,0:18:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你玩扑克这么厉害啊 为啥一直那么低调
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.27,0:18:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种雕虫小技 没必要显摆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱花也很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:40.38,sign 黑体,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42\frz350.292\3c&H414141&\pos(653,516)\c&HD6D6DA&}已调成振动模式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.83,0:18:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明脑子没我好使
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.15,0:18:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好不要和爱花两个人独处
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.49,0:18:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱花这丫头满脑子邪恶的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.41,0:18:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪恶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.85,0:18:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认识她起就一直这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.01,0:19:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道那家伙在想些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刻薄又不招人喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当时还想根本没法和这种女的一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.10,0:19:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 她不知不觉地就融入了我们家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.98,0:19:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉就融入进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.85,0:19:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 到底在想些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.08,0:19:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱花在想些什么 你很想知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.49,0:19:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 因为很邪恶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.97,0:19:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对爱花…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.75,0:19:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啥 这样算的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.69,0:19:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个星期的早餐都归你包了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真广那动物般的第六感 会不会察觉到我们的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.30,0:20:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话就永远没法接吻了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.63,0:20:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为你不能像个男人那样强硬一点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.17,0:20:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.15,0:20:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱花 这样很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱花…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.37,0:20:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:21:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱花…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向日葵们都在看着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱花…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.68,0:21:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野 差不多该上路了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.97,0:21:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.18,0:21:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我对魔具没什么兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过决战真让人热血沸腾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.70,0:21:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么害怕做啥 我怎么可能朝你开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决心不过是记忆的奴隶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.03,0:21:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随记忆可以幻化成万物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:56.27,Default 备注,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《哈姆雷特》中第三幕第二场台词
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.94,0:21:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈姆雷特吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:21:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天这复仇剧也该落幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.69,0:22:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.33,0:22:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎明的天空已裹上了赤褐色的外衣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.94,0:22:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踏着那东方高山上的露水走过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.33,0:22:13.57,Default 备注,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《哈姆雷特》第一章第一场台词
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.39,0:22:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.30,0:22:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.43,0:24:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得今天会有什么变化吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.91,0:24:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是决一雌雄的时候了 左门
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.02,0:24:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.45,0:24:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就让我来了断你的好运
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.81,0:24:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此这个世界会陨灭一次
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.64,0:24:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了啊 绝园之树
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.65,0:24:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要…只要能复仇就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.02,0:24:27.51,每集标题,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(563,484)}魔女断头之时
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.51,0:24:28.51,每集标题,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(595,576)}
